Step 1 - Unzip the Jacket and dramatically pull it open
Step 2 - Push your hands backwards to accentuate your athletic built
Step 3 - Swing the jacket off one of the sides in a sharp motion

‚Ä¢
istg, ISU could push their "best costume" awards all they want and designers could come up with photobooks about different impressive combinations of colors, sparkles and sequins but... there is something so magestic, so simple yet so satisfying about a plain, black training gear fitted perfectly to an athletic body! It deserves a whole new category of awards on its own. The training gear almost merging with its owner, highlighting what already exists underneath it; allowing you to concentrate on the precision, lines, angles, symmetry of the athlete's movements üñ§
‚Ä¢
The back of Yuzuru's training shirt reads the quote "CHALLENGE THE UNKNOWN!!" üí´
Yuzuru himself decides and designs the quotes that will be embroidered on his training gear. You can even see his name "Yuzuru H." on the collar of the shirt, in golden letters. He has new quotes every season and even changes through multiple quotes per season. I'm sure he specifically picks out which T-Shirt to wear, depending on the feeling he has at every competition, before each practice.
This quote resonates with Yuzuru's drive of never giving up, never feeling fully satisfied with what he has accomished in the past. "He has two Olympic gold medals, he has broken 19 records, he is already the biggest star of the sport in history, what else does he want???" well, he wants exactly that: to push further, explore and overcome new limits, TO CHALLENGE THE UNKNOWN! üí™
